### CODEBASE-MEMORY-MCP ACCESS

Index the repo first (required each run):
  codebase-memory-mcp cli index_repository '{"repo_path":"/workspace"}'

**Tools:**
  codebase-memory-mcp cli search_graph '{"name_pattern":"<regex>","label":"Function"}'
  codebase-memory-mcp cli search_code '{"text":"<term>"}'
  codebase-memory-mcp cli get_code_snippet '{"qualified_name":"<name>"}'
  codebase-memory-mcp cli trace_call_path '{"function_name":"<name>","direction":"both"}'
  codebase-memory-mcp cli query_graph '{"query":"MATCH (f:Function) WHERE f.name CONTAINS \"x\" RETURN f.name LIMIT 10"}'
  codebase-memory-mcp cli get_architecture

Do NOT read repository files directly. Do NOT commit, push, or modify files.
